The token contact address is 0xcD657182A749554fc8487757612F02226355269d.Thank you.Yes, i see that you can sell the token on Uniswap after scanning the contract address on Dextool. According to dextool, it has $42k liquidity and 5% tax for buy and sell. So its better you use more than 6% slippage to prevent transaction error.
